'''DF76-882''' was a [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]] [[Datafile/Legends|datafile]] that cataloged the various [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]], capital ship classes, and [[support craft]] used by the [[Yevetha]].

The datafile [[DF76-901]] was later appended to DF76-882 when new data became available.

